explanation: [0-0] In a bathroom with purple tiles, three colorful animated characters are sitting on three separate toilets. On the far left is an orange character with exaggerated big eyes and mouth, sitting on the toilet. In the middle is a green character lazily leaning against the toilet. On the far right is a blue character with a crown, sticking its tongue out and sitting on the toilet, looking unwell. On the wall behind them, three towels are neatly hung on a rack, each with a smiling face pattern in orange, green, and blue, respectively.

[0-10] The orange character jumps off the toilet, mouth wide open revealing its teeth, looking excited. It then jumps back onto the toilet. Next, the green character suddenly jumps up from the toilet, staying in the air for a brief moment, then stretching out its limbs, and finally landing on the towel rack behind. The orange character watches with its mouth wide open, in disbelief. Finally, the blue character jumps off the toilet, suspends in mid-air, mimicking the previous action of the orange character while maintaining a funny expression. It hangs in the air and then goes back up, repeating this several times before falling back into the toilet.
